OL,3,C'We've done it': Granada viewers help
OL,4,Cto give man with cerebral palsy a voice
OL,6,FA Liverpool fan with cerebral palsy is
OL,7,Ffinally able to communicate thanks to
OL,8,Fdonations from ITV Granada viewers.
OL,10,FRyan Edwards, from Wallasey, has
OL,11,Frequired round the clock care and a
OL,12,Fbreathing machine his entire life, but
OL,13,Fhis family say that's never stopped
OL,14,Fthe "bright and funny" 32-year-old
OL,15,Ffrom being the happy person he is.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
