OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776355854
OL,3,C'We've done it': Granada viewers help
OL,4,Cto give man with cerebral palsy a voice
OL,6,FHe is non-verbal and his family rely
OL,7,Fon visual cues to understand what he
OL,8,Fneeds, but that has changed thanks to
OL,9,Fa communication device that allowed
OL,10,Fhim to control a computer with his
OL,11,Feyes and have it speak aloud for him.
OL,13,FRyan's sister Samantha said: "It's
OL,14,Flike teaching someone to speak for the
OL,15,Ffirst time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
