FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776355854
OL,3,C'We've done it': Granada viewers help
OL,4,Cto give man with cerebral palsy a voice
OL,6,F"It's someone who has not been able to
OL,7,Fcommunicate their whole life beside
OL,8,Fyes and no, and all of a sudden they
OL,9,Fopen this pandora's box, and they can
OL,10,Fsay how they feel, they can describe
OL,11,Fthings, and now he's bossing us all
OL,12,Faround and telling us what to do,
OL,13,Fsaying naughty words."
OL,15,FUsing the device, Ryan said: "Thank
OL,16,Fyou so much for helping me find my
OL,17,Fvoice. Thanks to you all."
OL,19,FIt also allowed him to tell his mum he
OL,20,Floves her, and 'Happy Mothers Day' for
OL,21,Fthe first time ever.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
