PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776355854
OL,3,C'We've done it': Granada viewers help
OL,4,Cto give man with cerebral palsy a voice
OL,6,FRyan initially used the communication
OL,7,Fdevice as part of a three week trial,
OL,8,Fbut his family was then told he did
OL,9,Fnot meet the criteria to fund the
OL,10,Fequipment permanently.
OL,12,FHis family said they woke up one day
OL,13,Fand decided they would raise the money
OL,14,Fto fund the device themselves.
OL,16,FRyan and his sister appeared on ITV
OL,17,FGranada Reports in November 2025,
OL,18,Fsmashing through their #12,000 target
OL,19,Fto raise a total of #17,000.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
