FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776355854
OL,3,C'We've done it': Granada viewers help
OL,4,Cto give man with cerebral palsy a voice
OL,6,FSamantha said: "We were all watching
OL,7,Ftogether and then suddenly the
OL,8,FGoFundMe just kept going up and up and
OL,9,Fup. We finally hit the goal and I
OL,10,Fdon't think our section even finished
OL,11,Fand we'd hit the goal."
OL,13,F"We were just like 'oh my god we've
OL,14,Fdone it.' We were lost for words."
OL,16,FThe device is similar to a standard
OL,17,FPC, but the smart tech is in a camera
OL,18,Fwhich attaches to the screen and uses
OL,19,Finfra-red to detect Ryan's eye,
OL,20,Fallowing him to select words and
OL,21,Fphrases that are then said out-loud.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
