OL,3,C'We've done it': Granada viewers help
OL,4,Cto give man with cerebral palsy a voice
OL,6,FSamantha said it has not just changed
OL,7,Fhis life, it has changed the lives of
OL,8,Feveryone around him.
OL,10,FShe said: "I just want to thank
OL,11,Feveryone so much for opening up his
OL,12,Fworld".
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
